{
  "texts": [
    "We evaluated the classification results found with the proposed models: ViT and MLP-Mixer and compared it with the classification results reported in ref.",
    "In their research, the authors developed a network, referred to as MsGoF, to classify BUS tumors as malignant or benign.",
    "Moreover, they trained their method on three available datasets including the BUSI [21] dataset.",
    "A fivefold cross validation was utilized to fully evaluate the effectiveness of the method, with 20% of the training set used as a validation set.",
    "Our results were also compared with those reported in ref."
  ]
}